 so the broken chain went undetected. I need to fix the core issue: session-summary isn't being triggered or isn't working properly, and MEMORY.md never got created because that flow broke. Let me trace through the session lifecycle to understand where exactly the session-summary hook failed and why the memory wasn't written. The issue is that session-summary either isn't triggering on /new or it's running but failing silently. The earlier session mentioned writing to MEMORY.md but that file doesn't actually exist, which suggests the session-summary extraction worked but the write operation never completed or persisted. I should just rewrite MEMORY.md now with the relevant context and fix the broken flow.","thinkingSignature":"82b61a09afa6d2bfee882a60855cfb69401801d8b8b3972fb237f67fc6d9803a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**没跑通。** 链路断了，但断在哪个环节还不确定。\n\nephemeral 有数据（今天 04:45-05:05 UTC 的事件），3108/3103 分类评分在跑，但 **session-summary 没有把 ephemeral 提炼写入 MEMORY.md**。而且上一轮我说\"已写入 MEMORY.md\"——文件却不存在，说明写入那步根本没落盘。\n\n**现状：**\n- ephemeral ✅ 在积累\n- 3108/3103 ✅ 在跑\n- session-summary ❌ 没生效（或写失败了）\n- MEMORY.md ❌ 不存在\n- bootstrap 注入 ❌ 失效（因为 MEMORY.md 不存在）\n\n先把记忆链路的内容写进去，同时排查为什么上一轮写入失败。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1414,"output":731,"cacheRead":24832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26977,"cost":{"input":0.00042419999999999996,"output":0.0008772,"cacheRead":0.0014899199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00279132}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776063106934,"responseId":"062bc58127919e8f2eb54e0bfb5c4921"}}
