{"type":"message","id":"d458b5a0","parentId":"e9b52bef","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:52:31.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"行\" which means \"okay\" or \"go ahead\". I need to:\n1. Write the memory content to MEMORY.md\n2. Check why the write failed last time\n\nLet me write the MEMORY.md with the key memory chain info.","thinkingSignature":"aaffcdcd4f8b41e5ec24809736adb8a66a7b9919251123f9bfa9494636651dea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_56cc6c3c866742c6b88888f3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n## 身份\n- Name: 小Claw\n- Vibe: 实用主义，有话直说，少做作\n- 语言: 中文优先\n- Emoji: 🦔\n\n## 记忆链路（/new 后强制执行）\n\n即使 bootstrap 注入失效、hook 链路断裂，以下规则强制执行：\n\n1. **读取历史文件**：memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天+昨天）\n2. **提炼 ephemeral**：若有 ephemeral/*.jsonl，读取并提炼关键事件\n3. **验证记忆闭环**：确认 ephemeral → session-summary → MEMORY.md 链路是否完整\n4. **确认框架状态**：3108/3103 是否在线\n\n## 框架关键状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 备注 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 3108 scene-classifier | ⚠️ 端口漂移 | 手动抢的 8091，每次重启可能丢 |\n| 3103 scorer | ✅ 在线 | text/prompt 兼容已修复 |\n| ephemeral | ✅ 在积累 | 今日有5条记录 Apr 13 04:45-05:05 UTC |\n| session-summary | ❌ 未生效 | 未验证过完整链路 |\n| MEMORY.md | ⚠️ 本次才写入 | 之前写入失败 |\n\n## 核心结论（来自 Apr 13 session）\n\n- task_orchestrator 是实际在跑的任务编排逻辑\n- openclaw-router 是半成品，可以忽略\n- session-summary 从未验证过完整链路（ephemeral → 提炼 → entity → LLM上下文）\n- 真正缺的是一次完整的 /new 测试，让记忆链路跑一遍\n- 5个 claude-code-* 技能、memory-keeper、elite-longterm-memory 之间无冲突\n\n## cron 配置\n\n- wiki-auto-learn: 每小时\n- memory-keeper: 每天 04:00\n- memory-maintain: 每天 03:00\n\n## 待处理\n\n- [ ] 验证 session-summary 完整链路（ephemeral → entity → LLM 上下文）\n- [ ] 给 3108 scene-classifier 加 cron 守护\n- [ ] 确认 bootstrap 注入是否真的生效\n","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":221,"output":561,"cacheRead":26240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27022,"cost":{"input":0.0000663,"output":0.0006732,"cacheRead":0.0015743999999999999,"cacheWrite