{"type":"message","id":"dd254809","parentId":"95120d9f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T06:56:55.365Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that openclaw.json has a `hooks` section with entries for `self-improvement`, `context_hook`, and `auto-score-classify`. But I don't see `session-summary` or the bootstrap handler (handler.js) explicitly listed. Let me look at the hooks section more carefully.","thinkingSignature":"c4c53c640c652c75f84af1b62bdb1017b1924ff93094a2fe8fde9fc22cf30aae"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eccc09132e574a02929aa6cc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/ai/.openclaw/openclaw.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json\nd=json.load(sys.stdin)\nhooks = d.get('hooks', {})\nprint(json.dumps(hooks, indent=2))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":984,"output":130,"cacheRead":55104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56218,"cost":{"input":0.00029519999999999997,"output":0.000156,"cacheRead":0.00330624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00375744}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776063410445,"responseId":"062bc6b1b67e825fb88735b49c0daf35"}}
